\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Then he sat against a comfortable nook in the tree trunk and watched his mind as it slowly turned away from the shame of walking away from Vigram\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s. It was stupid of him to throw that away. How was he going to make money now? He\u8217\'92d probably have to sell himself to Geem.}
